text: Audrey Daule (born 6 May 1993) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * "Interview Audrey DAULE et Léa BACHELIER".
